714366f-a.title: Manhattan: 72nd Street (East) - Lexington Avenue
714366f-a.text:
158-162 East 72nd Street, adjoining and east of the S.E. corner
of Lexington Avenue. 160 is the Kingdom Gould residence, which has
recently been sold. The three houses are to be replaced in 1935
by an apartment building.
August 25, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
